\begin_inset Formula $z_{{\rm acc}}$
\end_inset

 (dashed lines).
 This is because 
\begin_inset Formula $z_{{\rm acc}}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $m_{{\rm vir}}/m_{{\rm acc}}$
\end_inset

 are correlated.
