\end_inset

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $z=0$
\end_inset

, where the host halos are split based on their concentrations.
 The solid lines are for the subhalos whose host halos have high concentration,
 while dashed lines correspond to the low-concentration host halos.
 All the host halos used here are greater than 
